reviews: I replaced some laces in jogger pants and used it as a belt for others with plenty of string left over. Holds up nicely and gives off that Fear of God aesthetic if you're into that.
its lasted me a long time, and has a mesh seperator inside to keep my cords/papers separate from my ink pens. Very roomy for its size and looks cool with my art supplies.

The lamp can only adjust in so many ways and you have to turn the base to turn it away. It is taller than expect but does the job plus having a usb to charge my phone is handy and suits my office aesthetic
it fit well + is a great basic, however it does come down a little in size so now it fits dead perfect, although i like them a bit bigger, will buy an XL next time

review_title: But nevertheless its at a good price & does the job of keeping me cozy
reviews: I have an original & this definitely isn't the same Carhart if ya know what I mean. But nevertheless its at a good price & does the job of keeping me cozy. It sits a little tall on the top so pull the back down generally.

review_title: It'll help if you want it to help
reviews: For the basic psychology course, it's what's going to make the difference of an A and A+ other than that you probably wouldn't really need it if you don't care that much lol.

This was a fantastic read! An original Aboriginal gothic story.
Insight into the beautiful, scary, spiritual and physical journey of an Indigenous girl trying to find her brother lost at sea and what it means to be Haisla woman. I think this book is important to west coast indigenous history and draws on such intimacy that you won't forget it.

review_title: carrying it around from place to place feels like a little much
reviews: I can appreciate it's use compared to using a trackpad on a mac (which gave me tendinitis in the first place) however, carrying it around from place to place feels like a little much, but it does save my wrist.. I like it, affordable and comfortable for a student!
Comfortable, affordable. I have tendinitis so this was definitely a necessary purchase. Arrived quickly too!
